Class Paperback

  • java.lang.Object
    • sait.bms.problemdomain.Books
      • sait.bms.problemdomain.Paperback

  • public class Paperback
extends Books
    Description: Books super class that holds all common attributes for sub classes of ChildrensBook, CookBook, Paperback, and Periodical books. This subclass generates an instance of a Paperback book.
